Tell HN: hnrss.org RSS Feeds Broken due to Algolia issue
text:
I subscribe to both the front page and comments feed via Feedly, and I don’t see any updates for the last day or so.

Investigating a bit, hnrss.org relies on Algolia search, and the crawler appears to be down: https://github.com/algolia/hn-search/issues/233

Tell HN: YouTube seems to have a bug regarding the thumbnail video durations
text:
Just noticed this.

https://youtube.com/@Petscop - It only appears to affect this one channel, though it could affect more.

If you read the thumbnail's duration value for some of the videos it will say that some are longer than an hour.

This is not true however, as upon clicking on the videos it seems that they're at most half an hour.

What's going on with YouTube here?
